column2: SELECT TOP #  ps.ra, ps.dec, ps.z,  ps.cx, ps.cy, ps.cz,  zoo.spiral, zoo.elliptical, zoo.uncertain,  ps.petroMag_r, pz.absMagR,  m1.mstellar_median, m1.warning,  m2.mstellar_median, m2.warning,  m3.logMass, m3.age, m3.SFR, m3.metallicity,  m4.logMass, m4.t_age, m4.age, m4.ssfr, m4.metallicity FROM SpecPhoto AS ps  JOIN zooSpec AS zoo ON zoo.objid = ps.objid  JOIN photoz AS pz ON pz.objid = ps.objid  JOIN specobj AS s ON s.bestObjID = ps.objid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM1# AS m1 ON m1.specObjID = ps.specObjID  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS m2 ON m2.specObjID = ps.specObjID  JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS m3 ON m3.specObjID = ps.specObjID  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust AS m4 ON m4.specObjID = ps.specObjID WHERE  ps.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND ps.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND ps.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND ps.zWarning = #  AND ps.petroMag_r < #  AND ps.type = #  AND zoo.spiral = # OR zoo.elliptical = #  AND pz.absMagR < #
